data.description: Beautifully well kept 3 bedroom home. Cozy living room with gorgeous hardwood floors and warm inviting wood burning stove. Bright, open kitchen with all Stainless Steel appliance, granite countertops, tiled back splash and breakfast peninsula. Dining room and breakfast nook area with sliders leading to oversized deck. Lower level offers a huge family room, full bathroom and laundry room with washer and dryer. Great yard and close to shops, schools and parks. Desired Minisink Valley School District.
